race.description: Tarcoola Express Drive Thru Coffee Mdn
race.comment: BLACK CILLA (5) disappointed here last start over the 1410m journey and drops back in trip today. She flew late over a similar trip first-up and that was the best performance we've seen from her. Likely to get back again but can fly over the top to shed her maiden tag. KIDDING ME (6) is a maiden galloper who hasn't raced since finishing 1.75 lengths back in seventh over 1000m at Pinjarra Scarpside prior to the spell. Her recent trial was very good and this rave looks to shape nicely for her. Ticks plenty of boxes and can resume on a winning note. REMEMBER WHEN (14) was out of the money when resuming from a spell last start over 1203m at this track. Open to further improvement now and with some luck he can be in the finish. DIXIE PRINCESS (3) is knocking on the door with his recent runs and gets the in-form apprentice on board. Can feature. BIG BOPPER (2) is not out of this with the blinkers on for the first time.
